261
00:13:40,875 --> 00:13:41,416
Please don't fire us!
Please don't fire us!

262
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:45,458
[SHINO groaning]

263
00:13:45,541 --> 00:13:46,500
[CLOCK meows]

264
00:13:49,208 --> 00:13:50,833
[gunshots]

265
00:13:52,916 --> 00:13:54,458
