Love stealer!

270
00:14:06,416 --> 00:14:08,333
Thanks for helping me practice.

271
00:14:08,416 --> 00:14:09,583
[RAIKA]
How could I say no?

272
00:14:09,666 --> 00:14:10,833
I've never seen you so excited

273
