for early morning
target shooting before!

274
00:14:13,375 --> 00:14:14,875
[AKARI] That gun battle
with Takachiho

275
00:14:14,958 --> 00:14:16,541
was a real wake-up call.

276
00:14:16,625 --> 00:14:19,958
