about this Raika thing.

293
00:14:53,458 --> 00:14:54,458
[RIKO]
Don't apologize.

294
00:14:54,541 --> 00:14:56,583
I'm happy to talk
to my old Amica.

295
00:14:56,666 --> 00:14:59,291
So your big worry is that
between her and Akari,

296
00:14:59,375 --> 00:15:01,583
things might be getting
a little too kissy-kissy?

297
00:15:01,666 --> 00:15:02,791
[KIRIN]
Exactly!

298
00:15:02,875 --> 00:15:04,625
And if those two become
attached at the hip,

299
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:06,625
