Grand Canyon-sized,

300
00:15:06,708 --> 00:15:09,583
well, canyon between
all four of us!

301
00:15:09,666 --> 00:15:11,541
Maybe she doesn't
take you seriously yet

302
00:15:11,625 --> 00:15:14,500
because you still belong
to CVR's Division Two.

303
00:15:14,583 --> 00:15:17,833
So how 'bout you
get her to say a manifesto?

304
00:15:17,916 --> 00:15:18,916
[KIRIN]
Oh!

305
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,208
[KIRIN]
Great plan!

306
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,916
[RAIKA]
Giving derringer training?

307
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,625
