me doesn't entice you enough,

311
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:34,375
all my classmates are very cute!

312
00:15:34,458 --> 00:15:36,458
See...?

313
00:15:36,541 --> 00:15:38,083
Don't you wanna see more?

314
00:15:38,166 --> 00:15:39,625
Come teach us.

315
00:15:40,666 --> 00:15:42,416
