how to shoot yet!

318
00:15:46,916 --> 00:15:48,458
Is that so...

319
00:15:48,541 --> 00:15:50,000
You're making excuses.

320
00:15:50,083 --> 00:15:52,958
Maybe you are the one
who's bad with smaller guns.

321
00:15:53,041 --> 00:15:54,666
You'd rather not
teach my friends at all

322
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:56,083
than make a mistake.

323
00:15:56,166 --> 00:15:57,458
What a selfish chicken!

324
00:15:57,541 --> 00:16:00,000
I am so not a chicken, you brat!

325
00:16:00,958 --> 00:16:01,958
So that's that.

326
00:16:02,041 --> 00:16:03,708
I'm not gonna be your teacher.

327
00:16:03,791 --> 00:16:04,625
No way.

328
00:16:04,708 --> 00:16:05,750
[KIRIN]
Really?

329
00:16:09,833 --> 00:16:11,250
[AKARI]
Don't be so hard on her.

330
00:16:11,333 --> 00:16:13,833
I think it'd be nice if
you helped out Kirin.

331
00:16:13,916 --> 00:16:16,333
[RAIKA] I'm not trying
to be mean, it's just that...

332
00:16:16,416 --> 00:16:17,708
Well... It's like...

333
00:16:17,791 --> 00:16:19,500
She's a lot of fun and all.

334
00:16:19,583 --> 00:16:21,916
But she totally acts like
she's the upperclassman,

335
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,541
ordering me to do
whatever she wants,

336
00:16:23,625 --> 00:16:25,000
whenever she wants.

337
00:16:26,416 --> 00:16:27,625
Now that you say that...

338
00:16:27,708 --> 00:16:29,166
Didn't she have a picture of her

339
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:30,958
that she made you
put in your room?

340
00:16:33,458 --> 00:16:34,750
Stop it!

341
00:16:34,833 --> 00:16:37,250
[AKARI] Be up front with her
about the relationship.

342
00:16:37,333 --> 00:16:38,958
[RAIKA]
Shut up about it!

343
00:16:39,041 --> 00:16:41,375
Why's she want me to teach
her stupid class, anyway?

344
00:16:41,458 --> 00:16:43,875
I can't handle a whole room
full of junior high crazies!

345
00:16:43,958 --> 00:16:46,041
I can't even handle her!

346
00:16:46,125 --> 00:16:48,708
[AKARI]
Huh... It is a little odd.

347
00:16:48,791 --> 00:16:50,833
I wonder what she's
trying to get outta this.

348
00:16:50,916 --> 00:16:52,708
[SHINO] Are you thinking
anything specific?

349
00:16:52,791 --> 00:16:54,791
[AKARI] No, it's more like
it's just a gut feeling

350
00:16:54,875 --> 00:16:56,208
that something's up.

351
00:16:56,291 --> 00:16:59,083
Look, the only way to find out
is to grant her request.

352
00:16:59,166 --> 00:17:01,000
Plus, doing it would
make her happy.

353
00:17:01,083 --> 00:17:02,916
No! And that is final!

354
00:17:04,125 --> 00:17:05,416
[KIRIN]
What?

355
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,000
You're gonna teach my class
how to shoot after all?

356
00:17:07,083 --> 00:17:08,625
Raika, you made my day.

357
00:17:08,708 --> 00:17:09,750
Thank you so much!

358
00:17:09,833 --> 00:17:11,625
Akari insisted
I help, so really,

359
00:17:11,708 --> 00:17:12,541
you should thank her.

360
00:17:12,625 --> 00:17:14,041
[KIRIN]
Akari did that?

361
00:17:14,125 --> 00:17:15,583
Don't give me
the credit for this.

362
00:17:15,666 --> 00:17:16,958
Yeah, but it's the truth.

363
00:17:17,041 --> 00:17:19,041
Well, I'm always happy
to accept kind words

364
00:17:19,125 --> 00:17:20,125
from a friend.

365
00:17:20,208 --> 00:17:21,333
Good luck, girls!

366
00:17:21,416 --> 00:17:24,166
[RAIKA] Good luck on
your training with Aria!

367
00:17:24,250 --> 00:17:25,541
You ignored my request,

368
00:17:25,625 --> 00:17:28,333
but after Akari talks to you,
you're suddenly all,

369
00:17:28,416 --> 00:17:31,458
"Oh, sure, Kirin, I'm happy to
teach derringer shooting."

370
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:35,166
[KIRIN]
It's not important right now.

371
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:36,500
Well, let's go!

372
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,083
My name's Rui!

373
00:17:41,166 --> 00:17:42,375
And I'm Kuu!

374
00:17:42,458 --> 00:17:43,625
I'm Moyu!

375
00:17:43,708 --> 00:17:45,083
And I'm Kira!

376
00:17:45,166 --> 00:17:46,625
Oh, uh... hi.

377
00:17:46,708 --> 00:17:48,083
Nice to meet you, girls.

378
00:17:50,125 --> 00:17:51,333
[RAIKA]
Now listen.

379
00:17:51,416 --> 00:17:53,666
Its bad range means
you don't aim a derringer.

380
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:56,000
You press it in
their gut and shoot.

381
00:17:56,083 --> 00:17:57,250
[ALL squeal]

382
