00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,458
Press and shoot!

390
00:18:07,541 --> 00:18:08,791
[ALL squeal]

391
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,541
[RAIKA] I mean it!
Pay attention!

392
00:18:10,625 --> 00:18:12,208
Guns are serious business!

393
00:18:21,125 --> 00:18:22,833
[ALL]
Thank you, Miss Raika!

394
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:25,333
[KIRIN]
We'll never forget the one day

395
00:18:25,416 --> 00:18:27,541
