fun and worthwhile.

396
00:18:27,625 --> 00:18:28,750
[RAIKA]
It's fine.

397
00:18:28,833 --> 00:18:31,583
But you'd be further
along if you listened.

398
00:18:31,666 --> 00:18:33,208
[KIRIN]
I almost forgot your gift!

399
00:18:33,291 --> 00:18:35,375
What? You don't
have to do that.

400
00:18:35,458 --> 00:18:36,791
The school is
supposed to pay me.

401
00:18:36,875 --> 00:18:37,958
Shut up and follow!

402
00:18:38,041 --> 00:18:39,250
[RAIKA]
What? Hey!

403
00:18:39,333 --> 00:18:41,125
[KIRIN] Right this way,
through these doors,

404
00:18:41,208 --> 00:18:43,250
