you could desire.

405
00:18:52,833 --> 00:18:54,250
[RAIKA]
What is this place?

406
00:18:54,333 --> 00:18:55,375
Hey, Kirin?

407
00:18:57,541 --> 00:19:01,125
[ALL] Welcome to
the CVR Training Room!

408
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:02,125
