452
00:20:36,875 --> 00:20:38,708
[RAIKA]
I take Kirin as my bride!

453
00:20:41,416 --> 00:20:43,291
[ALL]
Congratulations!

454
00:20:45,583 --> 00:20:46,625
[ALL]
