455
00:20:46,708 --> 00:20:47,750
[KIRIN laughing]

456
00:20:48,958 --> 00:20:51,333
[RAIKA]
Weirdest. Day. Ever.

457
00:20:52,541 --> 00:20:55,500
[AKARI] So how'd it go
teaching Kirin's class?

458
00:20:55,583 --> 00:20:56,541
Fine, I guess.

459
00:20:56,625 --> 00:20:58,708
