accident on the range?

460
00:20:58,791 --> 00:21:00,666
Well, no.

461
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:02,500
For now, I'll just say that...

462
00:21:02,583 --> 00:21:04,250
Everybody in our group
seems to be worried

463
00:21:04,333 --> 00:21:06,041
about the craziest things.

464
00:21:07,125 --> 00:21:09,541
[KIRIN]
Oh, big sister, Raika!

465
00:21:09,625 --> 00:21:11,708
Wait for your one true love!

466
00:21:12,375 --> 00:21:13,666
