477
00:21:33,166 --> 00:21:34,333
[AKARI]
Move in?

478
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,166
[RAIKA]
No!

479
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:38,500
No more games!

480
00:21:38,583 --> 00:21:40,250
[KIRIN groans]

481
00:21:40,333 --> 00:21:42,208
[KIRIN]
Oh hey, Akari, Shino!

482
00:21:42,291 --> 00:21:44,166
Yesterday after class,
I recorded Raika

483
00:21:44,250 --> 00:21:46,166
vowing to me that I'm her bride!

484
00:21:46,250 --> 00:21:47,208
[RAIKA]
I take Kirin--

485
00:21:47,291 --> 00:21:49,208
[KIRIN screams]

486
00:21:52,208 --> 00:21:53,000
