487
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:54,250
I knew they were close,

488
00:21:54,333 --> 00:21:56,416
but I didn't know things
were moving so quickly.

489
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:57,583
[SHINO]
Hold me.

490
00:21:57,666 --> 00:21:59,625
Let's try to be as close
as they are, okay?

491
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:01,125
