00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:20,541
[KIRIN] She acts like
she's embarrassed.

499
00:22:20,625 --> 00:22:22,041
But she loves it.

500
00:23:54,583 --> 00:23:56,833
[SHINO] You're accused of
forcing yourself on Akari!

501
00:23:58,458 --> 00:23:59,625
I find you guilty!

502
00:23:59,708 --> 00:24:01,083
[TAKACHIHO] There was
no forcing of anything,

503
00:24:01,166 --> 00:24:03,166
and you were creeping!

504
00:24:03,250 --> 00:24:04,916
You are guilty!

505
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:06,208
[TAKACHIHO]
